name: Tezzy Everydays #6 | Tezervoir Dogs | May 12th, 2021
description: This is the sixth day of my 1 of 1 pixel art series. Every pixel art piece will involve everyones favorite coin, which most certainly is Tezos. I decided to rock some Tarantino inspired pixel art today, as he's one of my favorite directors and Reservoir Dogs is such a perfect film. As a late teen in the late 90's, I would stay up all night and watch Bravo. They would often play films like Reservoir Dogs, 400 Blows and many more. Tezzy Everydays are created by @clipdad_
